    "---\n",
    "## Section 1: Imports and Configuration\n",
    "\n",
    "All libraries are imported in a single cell at the start of the notebook. This follows\n",
    "good practice by making all dependencies immediately visible and avoiding repeated imports\n",
    "scattered throughout the code. File paths and URLs are also defined here as constants so\n",
    "they only need updating in one place.\n",
    "\n",
    "- **pandas / numpy:** core data manipulation and numerical operations\n",
    "- **matplotlib / seaborn:** data visualisation\n",
    "- **requests:** HTTP download with custom headers to bypass server restrictions\n",
    "- **zipfile / os:** file extraction and disk cleanup"
   ]
